\id PHP - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG Philippians 01 14/2/91 Macnaughtan
\h PILIPAI
\toc1 Polomaęž‰ Pilipai Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\toc2 Pilipai
\toc3 Pilipai
\mt1 Polomaęž‰ Pilipai Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 IĚ± Polo make Timodi dikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaaso hataęž‰ mo Pilipai nane haleme Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ siosi you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ dikoni haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make iki Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ do wape pea tapaasopaęž‰me.
\v 2 Nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso yaapomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make mo puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki make kinaęž‰e.
\s1 Polomaęž‰ yeni peaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 3 Iki hone u moneaaso pitaęž‰maęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ikinaęž‰ keiyae pi laęž‰tiki pu halome.
\v 4 Kutupa ikinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yeni peaaso pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ hataęž‰ peatiki pu halome.
\v 5 Pa ekipeke mo ambaęž‰ hande titi panake paęž‰taęž‰ kone kini pea aęž‰pa ame do natenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo walono ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ mimi hau manunaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kini piaęž‰ etaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso ipilie natenaęž‰ poko paeyaaluekemaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa pokolo ombu halieke hone ulume. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ya pukimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ iki hone u halome.
\v 7 Koto taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Do Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰leke pokolo e seliapotaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ apaęž‰tao pokolomaęž‰me. Ame do IĚ± dipula pilu pitaęž‰maęž‰ make ambaęž‰ pa pomu haowaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ honkopu haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ ya pimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ litolo hombo peao halo ekitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao hataęž‰ pu halomaęž‰me.
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make mandake tupaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰pa haowee hone u halome. IĚ±maęž‰ do alo pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi aloeki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 9-10 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki yeni peao halome. Mo yeni peao halo ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke titinaęž‰ hau maĚ±leke liaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make ikaęž‰ otaęž‰eki homeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki make ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ teli pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make mandakenaęž‰ daeyolo daeyolo ombu haenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do yeni peaasome. Koto haumanu iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ daeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Ketiso ipilie natenaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ haumanu na pu hoeyao aletaęž‰ na piki wandaęž‰hali halimikie.
\v 11 Kutu pilie ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ halemeeki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo Yesu Ketiso homekemaęž‰ puemenaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ hau manumaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ tumbaalieke. Iki tumbaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto haumaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi lao yeiyaęž‰ laalieke.
\s1 Mo Polonaęž‰ dipula pitieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo kende tupaęž‰ winaęž‰ leekeeki
\p 
\v 12 Ya Ketiso yankeke tonuo IĚ±maęž‰ ya hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ mo hande IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa piaęž‰ ekimanu hone uemenaęž‰e. Koto hande hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo saęž‰saęž‰ na pitaęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ kende tupaęž‰ winaęž‰ alaęž‰me.
\v 13 Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Sisanaęž‰ da handeteke haleme aęž‰ndeli miniki haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make pa do haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaaso hali halo ekinaęž‰ dipula mea pitalemeke handelememe.
\v 14 Koto mo Ketiso yankeke tonu anekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehali hone wotu tulaenaęž‰ ya dipula pilu ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki wele peaalaęž‰me. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto paeyao paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke pipitaęž‰ pa pua hataęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki pu halememe.
\p 
\v 15 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo mandane ape ape lo haleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pitolo hataęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pi walo halememe. Patetaęž‰ pa mo mandane haliweki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone witolo hataęž‰ walo halememe.
\v 16 Ame do loaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Pi Seliapotaęž‰ honkopu haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ mo pimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ litolo hombo peao halaęž‰ hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me hone wilimime. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo pi walo halememe.
\v 17 Mo hande ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ loaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ epeke hone na wiki pa ikaęž‰ biki homeke daeyaluekemaęž‰ yeke pi walo halememe. Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do dipula pitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mandaneeki minaęž‰e laa pi walo halememe.
\v 18 Koto paęž‰laęž‰patetaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pitaęž‰ piaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ waleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolome. Epeke hone witolo piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make o epeke hone na witolo piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Pinaęž‰e. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo ombu halueke.
\s1 Pa ekiaęž‰ndaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ waleke wilieke
\p 
\v 19 Pa ekipeke mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni peao halemeke mo Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ temokomaęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make IĚ±taęž‰ dipula da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pomu halueke hone ulume.
\v 20 Ya peawee laa hone tieke paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ pokono Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ etaęž‰ otaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰laake nate paeyao make otaęž‰ ame do dipula pilu pitaęž‰ make otaęž‰ pipitaęž‰ pa pua hapeke yelieke la alome. Kutaataęž‰ IĚ± homoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make o pa hao haoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make ya halo hau paeyaomaęž‰ mo Ketiso yeiyaęž‰ lao halueke.
\v 21 Pa hao haoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaapeke ekinaęž‰ waleke wiliepate homono lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa mo hakaęž‰taęž‰pao wialaęž‰eki mulueke.
\v 22 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate pa ya hao halue ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke e mandaneeki piaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ handoeki maĚ±leke luaęž‰pe mone mataęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 23 Ale yaapomaęž‰ yolaęž‰ alu pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Do kenkenaęž‰ haloeki minaęž‰paęž‰lao Ketiso yaapo pua hapeketaęž‰ hone wotu paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make do polueke alo ekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epekeeki yaęž‰laęž‰pate
\v 24 IĚ±maęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ pa hao halo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tumiki haue.
\v 25 IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ koto hone witolo hataęž‰ pa hao halueke hone witolome. Ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hone tulaalemeeki daeyao honkopu hao hamenaęž‰ tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± paa halueke.
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ± mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰pa halumaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ laasemeeki daeyaenaęž‰ lelieke.
\s1 Aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 27 Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapomaęž‰ puemenaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ pu haleme hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ tumiki haue. Kutu pilimipate IĚ± epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make o pa ikaęž‰ pilimi haunaęž‰ pi lalimieki opuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ takaęž‰lao haemekaęž‰taęž‰me hone ulueke. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapo paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke hone wia hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ mualualu pu haemekaęž‰taęž‰me hone ulueke.
\v 28 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke hoto paeyao aelaęž‰ bao hapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ aelaęž‰ baalo peleme ekitaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pate haumaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰eki yelieke. Koto pate hau handolotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki otaęž‰ bepolaalimikie hone wilimikie. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ wele homekemaęž‰ bepolao halimikie.
\v 29 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokawamenaęž‰ yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke waleke kaęž‰laęž‰me. Do e pokawaluekemaęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ hone tulaaso ombu halo peleme ekimaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa Ketiso ipikaęž‰ haunaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ make meawaso ombu halimi ekimaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokalimikie.
\v 30 Ametaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tunao hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo ambaęž‰ hande pueke handeme aęž‰ndaęž‰ kone alome. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ame mo opiteleme aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ koto mandake aęž‰ndaęž‰ kone pa pu halome.
\c 2
\s1 Homu pu alualu piaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Ikaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekitaęž‰ iki honkopu hamenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰pe o ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone bamenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰pe o ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halemepe o ikaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homolo epeke hau pu alualu pelemepe.
\v 2 Kutu pu haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone mandake wilimieki tekenaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ mandake pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu peleme ekinaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ mandake hone peleme ekinaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ homeke hone wilimi ekinaęž‰ make kotoeki paeyaomaęž‰ IĚ± taęž‰naęž‰ wopu homaęž‰ tiaamenaęž‰ iki sutiaasome.
\v 3 Kutupa make nakaęž‰ honumake homeke hone witolo o honumake hau o handaenaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ iki paeyao homu pu alualu pea hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hau lombei paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone u hapaęž‰peke.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ pa nakaęž‰eki homeke hone witolo maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ leke tankemaęž‰ na handeke wopu hone wia handeteke ha alualu peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\s1 Ketisomaęž‰ homu pea hayeke ekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laeyekeeki
\p 
\v 5 Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ pu haleme hau manutaęž‰ mo hande Yesu Ketiso ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ pu hayeke hau leke kone piaęž‰paęž‰peke alee.
\q1 
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau leke kone pu hayekepate pa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ya Apaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hapeke ekitaęž‰ ya welemaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mulueke hone na wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 7 Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ hone pieke ekinaęž‰ hataęž‰ hande Apaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hapeke ekitaęž‰ pa winaęž‰ kone do kenkenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaaso halinaęž‰ hau leke miekeme. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ kenke hali leke aęž‰paataęž‰ kenke hali tupaęž‰ hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 8 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki kone homu pea hataęž‰ mo homolo polo pieke ekinaęž‰ na kiake mea homeekeme. Hande ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 9 Koto haumanu piekeeki tekenaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hali haenaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyao otaęž‰ biki paeyao lombeipiki biki kone haleekeme.
\q1 
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu yeiyaęž‰ laaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hepeni nane haleme ale manumaęž‰ make do kenke nane haleme ale manumaęž‰ make o kenke oto nane haleme ale manumaęž‰ make kotoeki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ tumiki yotu hao pandaęž‰ pilimikie.
\q1 
\v 11 Kutupa mo Ateke halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ laaluekemaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ paeyao opinaęž‰ peneme yaaso hataęž‰ Yesu Ketiso ipiki homeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Tekehalie laa lelimikie.
\s1 Do kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali
\p 
\v 12 Ya yankeke tonuo. Hande IĚ±maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake haomaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ya kakenaęž‰ homo haeme ekitaęž‰ epeaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ IĚ± iki ameĚ±leĚ± na halo dinaęž‰ ya kakenaęž‰ pa homo halimi ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ haue. Ikaęž‰ Ketiso haleme ekitaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ make pututumaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pu paeyaaluekemaęž‰ hone wopu u hapaęž‰peke.
\v 13 Kotaęž‰ pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki peawaluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone pinaęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ e pokolo ombu halaęž‰me.
\v 14-15 Do kenkenaęž‰ hoihoi piki hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ hoke haumanu na talo yako pea Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tikitiki piki wekiwandiki haluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hau paeyaonaęž‰ la la pu ape ape na leke hao hapaęž‰peke. Mo hande hoihoi piki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande deto halaęž‰ pi la halolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ oli hande hombulankaęž‰ to halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hapaęž‰peke alee.
\v 16 Koto hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikinaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ paa epolo paęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ ya paleke na hake halo polo ekinaęž‰ teke wilieke. Kotaęž‰ pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto peleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ya pokoaęž‰ etaęž‰ pa hameke e na pokeaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lolo pelemeeki walieke.
\p 
\v 17 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lia halo haemeke tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ kone pu halememe. Koto pu halemeeki mandaataęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitolo ya we holaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolome. Pinaęž‰e. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolomaęž‰me.
\v 18 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\s1 Timodi tapaalo piekeeki
\p 
\v 19 Ikaęž‰ pimanu aęž‰pa mokaęž‰lalieeki opitolo hataęž‰ IĚ± saęž‰saęž‰ peaenaęž‰ mo Tekehali Yesu ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰lekeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hosiki hao Timodi iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaaluekemaęž‰ hone witolome.
\v 20-21 Mandane wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ honumake honumake hone homeke u halemepate pa mo Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na u halememe. Kutu pu halemepate Timodimaęž‰ homeke homeketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ witolo hone mandake witolo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa hao halaęž‰me.
\v 22 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make Timoditaęž‰ handolotaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke halie la handelememe. Kutupa make aęž‰talaęž‰ leke hataęž‰ Timodi dikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo daeyaenaęž‰ poko hapaęž‰ etaęž‰ hone wilimime.
\v 23 Kutaataęž‰ pa titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ eki haumanu ipiliepe la handataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± epenaęž‰ tapaaluekemaęž‰ hone witolome.
\v 24 Kutupa make Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ waleke kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki handuluekemaęž‰ IĚ± make hosiki hao ipulueke.
\s1 Epaęž‰pototaitisi tapaali pieke pi
\p 
\v 25 Ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke Epaęž‰pototaitisi iki nane epenaęž‰ otaęž‰ tapaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone ulume. Ipikitaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo mandakenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaaso hataęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ haopaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi lawaasaęž‰ hali make hayaęž‰me.
\v 26 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki aĚ±iĚ± handuluekemaęž‰ hone wotu u halaęž‰me. Kutupa ipiki yeni haasaęž‰me pi opelemeeki opitolo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ puki tandamaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 27 Otaęž‰e ipikitaęž‰ yeni tieke mea otaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ homeaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeaęž‰me. Pa ipiki homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ puki tanda maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homonoyeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeaęž‰me.
\v 28 Koto piaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaaluekemaęž‰ hone tieke wotu paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paa ipilieki handolotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ paa homilimikie kutupa ya kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homoloeki make pa paeyaalieke.
\v 29 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ yankekeo laa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homa mo Tekehalinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ handa meaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ piaęž‰ hau tupaęž‰ pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u hapaęž‰peke.
\v 30 Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaaluekemaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipiki homaapaęž‰naęž‰ hone na wieke ekimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ tekepaęž‰taęž‰ homeekepate piekeme. Kutupiki hautaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ meaęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pealuekemaęž‰ piekeme.
\c 3
\s1 Otaęž‰ tikitiki hasaęž‰ hau
\p 
\v 1 Ya Ketiso yankeke tonuo. Ya pi lo paeyaaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ dupa alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ tunao hataęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke. Ambaęž‰ hande wape puaęž‰eki paa wape puluekemaęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pate iki lopaamaęž‰naęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pinaęž‰e hone witolo ekinaęž‰ paa wape pitolome.
\p 
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kikamaęž‰ leke hoke haumanu puluekemaęž‰ taapolo hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ loke yonkeleke kialuekemaęž‰ hoto paeyao hone u haleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke.
\v 3 Mo hau pu haleme haliweki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ patetaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ sekemesaisi hautaęž‰ mea halomaęž‰me. Pa ekipape. Nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yakopiki temokomaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minolo haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu halomaęž‰me. Kutupataęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunao hataęž‰ paleke na hao halomaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo nikaęž‰ manda loke ninaęž‰ peaaseme haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ hone otaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ ti lao na halomaęž‰me.
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ koto haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hone ti lao hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke alo. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo manda loke ninaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti lao hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki otaęž‰ ankulapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone witolome.
\v 5 Ya mendieke nate pulaęž‰ homeke yapeeke dinaęž‰ IĚ± sekemesaisi hau peaemekeme. IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ Isulai hali hano Isulai nane mendiekeme. IĚ±taęž‰ Benisamininaęž‰ tapakee. Kutupa ya apaęž‰naęž‰ atekenaęž‰ ateketaęž‰ mo Hibulu haliweki homeke haemekeme. Hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu miniki haasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi hotumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Paęž‰tisi hali haowaęž‰me.
\v 6 Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ hone wopu witolo hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tanda halaęž‰tiki pu haowaęž‰me. Homekemaęž‰ mo hande pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao miniki haasaęž‰ haumaęž‰ tikitiki haasaęž‰ hali hapeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pu hoeyaowaęž‰me.
\v 7 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaluekemaęž‰ yeke mo hande ya biki wiaęž‰ alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ pa alee hone ulume.
\v 8 Koto alemanu homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ya pu haowaęž‰ hau paeyao tapaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa alee hone witolome. Pa ekipeke. Mo otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ ya Tekehali Yesu Ketiso handuluekemaęž‰ yeke alome. IĚ±taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali homeke haluekemaęž‰ yeke ya pu haowaęž‰ hau paeyao kiao baowaęž‰me. Ketiso ya Tekehali haenaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea haluekemaęž‰ yeke mo hande hau paeyaotaęž‰ pa mo pa tana baasaęž‰ punku piki alemanue hone witolome.
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo tikitiki yao halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ya kone na polome. Hande Mosesimaęž‰ mieke Lo Pimanu opua pu hao meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ na polome laa loaęž‰me. Mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasome wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ku hala tikitiki yao halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ame molome. Do tikitiki yao haasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ekie.
\v 10 Ya hone paęž‰laęž‰eki homeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketiso handuluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Ketiso ipikaęž‰ tialaęž‰ wele paęž‰laęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tanda mieke tupaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ make kutupa Ketiso homeeke tupaęž‰ IĚ± make mandake tupaęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 11 Dupitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ya homulue ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ bepolao IĚ± paa mea tialieke hone witolo ya hone ti lao halome.
\s1 Tombo muluekemaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya puaęž‰peke hau
\p 
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰ koto haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ anaęž‰lao ambaęž‰ mea hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me pi na alome. IĚ±maęž‰ mo kitaęž‰laęž‰ epeke ale miono Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ IĚ± mea halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ koto ale muluekemaęž‰ honkopu pa haaso ombu halome.
\v 13 Ya yankeke tonuo. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ alome ya honemaęž‰ mo hande hautaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na molome hone witolopate pa dupiki hau homeke pitolome ya putia epoaęž‰ haumanu paeyao hone yonkaęž‰lao minaęž‰paęž‰laapaęž‰laa puaęž‰tiki mo mulu polo ale muluekemaęž‰ honkopu hoke hao pulume.
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hotonelinaęž‰ yenki muluekemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo tombo halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki aĚ±iĚ±ya pulume. Do ekinaęž‰ alome. Oli hepeni nane hao hapekeeki miono Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ IĚ± wi laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ alome.
\p 
\v 15 Niki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ takaęž‰lake temoko pilaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kutupiki haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone u hamanaęž‰ peaęž‰peke aleo. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate do wape tapaaso wandaęž‰hali iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ koto piki haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tikitiki yao u tialieke.
\v 16 Eki hau pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ mea putia epomaęž‰ hau tupaęž‰ kone ame do ane make koto hau tupaęž‰ kone puaęž‰tiki pomanaęž‰e.
\p 
\v 17 Ya yankeke tonuo. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pitolo hau hondo hapaęž‰peke. Mo hande puemenaęž‰ walomaęž‰ tikitiki haumanu pu haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ epeke haumanu ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handa honduluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u hapaęž‰peke.
\v 18 Ame do lolo polo pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoto eleke eleke wopu la ku haowaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ eĚ± alo alo hataęž‰ paa ta la kitolo handaęž‰e. Mandane wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ pu haleme haumaęž‰ kone mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki ti manda Ketiso homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkulao haenaęž‰ lo haleme.
\v 19 Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu teliolo hataęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniao haleme ekinaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua hao halimikie. Mo ikaęž‰ yaalomaęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ hau pu halemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ hakoko lu halememe. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa do kenkenaęž‰ hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hau leke pu halememe.
\v 20 Koto paęž‰laęž‰patetaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hepeni kenkenaęž‰ teke wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ epenaęž‰ yeke taęž‰naęž‰ lulu hataęž‰ yu wia halomaęž‰me.
\v 21 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ dete piki tande polo paęž‰laęž‰ loke manutaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki paĚ±aĚ± pupapeke lokemaęž‰ handekeeki topo peao hawalieke. Koto hautaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao lu tumbapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ welemaęž‰ peawalieke.
\c 4
\s1 Peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu
\p 
\v 1 Ya yankeke tonuo. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hande loaęž‰ pimanu paeyao hone witolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ takaęž‰lao hao hapaęž‰peke. O ya yankeke tonuo. Ikitaęž‰ ya puki piki wandaęž‰halie. IĚ±maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ hone wopu paęž‰laęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiao halememe. IĚ±maęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ paleke na hao halome.
\p 
\v 2 Yuodia neke make o Sindiki neke make IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opuaęž‰pe. Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso hakilaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ hone homeke u hapenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiliki hone u tiaasome.
\v 3 Kutupa ya Ketiso taęž‰maęž‰ni epekeo. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ hone homeke winaęž‰ tambaęž‰ miaęž‰peke alome. Pa ekipeke mo wandaęž‰ yaapo make Kaęž‰lemiti make mo ya e mandake pokolomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ peo lao daeyaenaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± weleke we wopu pea e tieke pokomaęž‰me. Koto wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki paeyaotaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ deto halaęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ wape pa ulaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 4 Ikaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homu hapaęž‰peke. Paa make alome. Taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homu hapaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 5 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pilimi hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ homu piki hau walo hapaęž‰peke. Mo Tekehalitaęž‰ niki teke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me.
\v 6 Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone witeleme ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo na yoko hapaęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu kinaęž‰ keiyae alo hataęž‰ honke lo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± tunao haseme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone wilimieki otaęž‰ lombeipiki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ puki lopaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone puki yaapo hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hao halieke.
\p 
\v 8 Ya yankeke tonuo. Ya paeyaaso pitaęž‰ dupa alome. Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ mo epeke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu make mo yeiyaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu make kotaęž‰ haumanu homeke hone u moneao hapaęž‰peke. Dupiki haunaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki leke tendepiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki tikitiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±leke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki hau seliapo seliapo pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yole hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make koto haumanu paeyao homeke hone u hamenaęž‰ alome.
\v 9 Mo hande IĚ±maęž‰ la kueke opua mimi manaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ pu hapaęž‰peke. Ya pimaęž‰ loeke opimi tupaęž‰ make ya haumaęž‰ pueke handeme tupaęž‰ make otaęž‰ pu hapaęž‰peke. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ puki lopao hamono lo halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao halieke.
\s1 Ikaęž‰ pa halemeke ale mea keiyae leeke pi
\p 
\v 10 O IĚ±maęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ halo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ wopu homolome. Pa ekipeke. Mo nate eleke eleke wopu paeyaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki paa waluekemaęž‰ potaęž‰ handaęž‰ wimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± hone yonkaęž‰laememe pi na alopate pa mo ikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki walaęž‰peke potaęž‰ na handaęž‰ witolo piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me alome.
\v 11 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ honumake hali halome hone witolo hataęž‰ do pi na alome. Pa ekipeke. Mo ya halo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki tupaęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ hone ulume.
\v 12 Mo miniki hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu otaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ hau pitaęž‰ mo aneke hapu hakaęž‰taęž‰pao miniki hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ hau yaapotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epeeke pea handa hone ulume. IĚ±maęž‰ aneke hapu noluekemaęž‰ make teaęž‰maęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ make aneke hapu hakaęž‰taęž‰pao wia haluekemaęž‰ make hosikieki siki wia haluekemaęž‰ make nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ do hau paeyaotaęž‰ handa halo ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ hone witolome.
\v 13 Do hau paeyaotaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ welemaęž‰ bepolatia aęž‰pa polome.
\p 
\v 14 Koto polopatetaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ya kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰ ekimanu tambaęž‰ mimi ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau pimime.
\v 15 Iki Pilipai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapo waloaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Maęž‰sedonia minaęž‰paęž‰lao poaęž‰ dinaęž‰ koto pitaęž‰maęž‰ siosi tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke IĚ± tambaęž‰ mumaęž‰me laa otaęž‰ hone witolo pitememe. Siosi tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ manimaęž‰ IĚ± otaęž‰ na tambaęž‰ mimipate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke koto hau pimime.
\v 16 IĚ± mo Desalonaika hataęž‰ hoto yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ± mani diaęž‰yaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ tapaatiki pu haememe.
\v 17 Ikaęž‰ pa hameke kiteleme alemanu muluekemaęž‰ pa na weitolo patetaęž‰ pa mo oli hepeni nane ikaęž‰ epeke haumanu pitelemeeki diminaęž‰laęž‰eki hakaęž‰taęž‰pawao wiaenaęž‰yeke hone paęž‰leke handa iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleke kitolo alome.
\v 18 Do wapenaęž‰ alo pitaęž‰ mo hande ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kimi alemanu molo ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alome IĚ±maęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao molo ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰e alome. Ametaęž‰ mo hande Epaęž‰pototaitisimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pa kiteleme alemanu paeyao mea aęž‰paeyeke handa ya wia halo polo ale manutaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ molome. Koto pa keleme ale manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ totopo yolepiki halaęž‰laęž‰ alemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki alemanu minolotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 19 Ya Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ aneke hapu hakaęž‰taęž‰pao ulaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ anaęž‰lao ku halieke.
\v 20 Nate paeyao nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lao hamanaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.
\p 
\v 21 Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali iki paeyao IĚ±maęž‰ iki hone witolo hataęž‰ aęž‰taloe laęž‰neaasome. Do IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandake haleme Ketiso yankeke tonumaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe laęž‰neaasememe.
\v 22 Kutupa do haleme Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe laęž‰neaasemepate mo Sisanaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe pi otaęž‰ wopu laęž‰neaasememe.
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki iki homeke homeke ameĚ±leĚ± nate paeyao u haenaęž‰e alome. 
